Parliament, Tuesday, 02 July 2019 – The Portfolio Committee on Public Works and Infrastructure will tomorrow be briefed by Agrément SA, Independent Development Trust (IDT), Construction Industry Development Board (CIDB) and the Council for the Built Environment (CBE) on their annual performance plans.
	
	Details of the meeting:
	Date: Wednesday, 03 July 2019
	Time: 09:30
	Venue: Good Hope Chamber, Good Hope Building
	.
	ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON PUBLIC WORKS AND INFRASTRUCTURE, MS NOLITHA NTOBONGWANA.
	
	For media enquiries, please contact the committee’s Media Officer:
	Name: Ms Faith Ndenze
